{"tid":1238831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃毓民：612就算使用了暴力都不是暴力！一個都唔告得暴動！告親圍佢！","createTime":"2019-06-18T03:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T05:50:37.000Z","uid":219007,"like":99,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4a4c759eff6c46fd9167dd9a534ab1f11d8e30","tid":1238831,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:10:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/34T-zGLUL8Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F34T-zGLUL8Q&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=c995b2ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/34T-zGLUL8Q</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重點：<br />\n<br />\n1. 幾百萬人既示威政府冇冧到其實好悲哀<br />\n<br />\n2.香港人現時乜都未贏到，唔好打飛機<br />\n<br />\n3.遲黎好過無黎，泛民起碼都醒覺政府亂用暴動罪，但如果2016初一泛民一早肯聲援，今日就唔洗咁慘有人坐冤獄！<br />\n<br />\n4.就算612使用了暴力都不是暴動，肢體衝突一定包含暴力，難道咁就暴動？ 一個都不能告暴動，告親圍佢！<br />\n<br />\n5.唔好打飛機，應立即設下死線，訂下進一步行動！<br />\n<br />\n6.請各位不要再在示威中提甚麼血債票賞選舉踢走保皇黨等，因為在現時比例代表制下，加上他們的選舉機器，不要忘記還有DQ手段，建制派的基本盤是不會大規模減少，還有看記錄泛民以往在議會抗爭根本無力，所以若泛民等人若慾在今次百萬人運人仲掛住lam票是十分下賤。"},{"pid":"4fce05932efd872847cabc470e00b04f715c0691","tid":1238831,"uid":258927,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U4rguvu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU4rguvu.jpg&h=f7216136&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a0b6c691e6c38ed99aea9d053b6f5dca09c50a9","tid":1238831,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:11:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c3cebb2a740c71662b7c498695e802d27ce4882","tid":1238831,"uid":225760,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:13:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a782ee4fcf08bd7094e83b170f8b96c53216a22","tid":1238831,"uid":254371,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:14:06.000Z","msg":"又鳩up"},{"pid":"0d27872d94d90e2d99ddbaae9b1a47a6ec08f80e","tid":1238831,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":1